data.description: PRICE REDUCTION!  SELLER PAYS $5,000 IN CLOSING COSTS at FULL PRICE. THIS BEAUTIFUL HOME IS SURROUNDED BY LAKES AND PARKS. This home has been freshly painted. Bonus in-law suite/guest house/office/apartment can be completed by new owner. Preferred Lender- Today's Financing-205-329-8988.  Other Lenders of your choice are welcome, also.  BUYER MUST INSURE THEMSELVES AND VERIFY ALL INFORMATION SCHOOLS, TAXES, ETC. SOLD AS-IS.
